<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 17 日星期三 15:30:07 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[West's Price Ceiling Caves in: Russian Oil Exports Hit Post-February 2022 High]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">当以美国为首的西方国家对俄罗斯石油征收价格上限时，他们希望限制碳氢化合物的出口，以剥夺莫斯科的收益来为其旨在保护顿巴斯免受基辅侵略的特殊军事行动提供燃料。然而，正如国际能源署的一份新报告所显示的那样，这些假设是完全错误的。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">根据 IEA 的数据，俄罗斯仍然是 OPEC+ 框架中最大的国家之一，4 月份原油日产量保持在 960 万桶，仅次于沙特阿拉伯。也就是说，出口量创下 2022 年 2 月后的新高，在 4 月达到每天 830 万桶的峰值。与此同时，俄罗斯碳氢化合物收入稳步增长，4 月份达到 150 亿美元，而 3 月份为 133 亿美元。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">正如 IEA 的专家所说，“俄罗斯似乎很容易为其原油和石油产品找到愿意购买的买家。”克里姆林宫官员一直警告说，俄罗斯不会违背其公民的最大利益行事，因此拒绝与敌对国家做生意，而是将碳氢化合物出口转向亚洲。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="infographics"><div class="article__infographics-media  m-border" data-uid="1110419699"><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="desktop"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="Oil Market Report  (Desktop) - Sputnik International" title="石油市场报告（桌面版）" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110418929.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="mobile"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="Oil Market Report (Mobile) - Sputnik International" title="石油市场报告（手机）" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110419107.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 15:22:05 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/wests-price-ceiling-caves-in-russian-oil-exports-hit-post-february-2022-high-1110419698.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/wests-price-ceiling-caves-in-russian-oil-exports-hit-post-february-2022-high-1110419698.html<category>多媒体</category><category>资料图</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>油</category><category>国际能源署 (IEA) </category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Nutcracker: What We Know About Russia's Kinzhal Hitting US Patriot System in Kiev]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110418058" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/106428/23/1064282303_0:0:3236:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_d089929321b175bbca0ee9d137d80885.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1064282302" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/nutcracker-what-we-know-about-russias-kinzhal-hitting-us-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110418058.html?share-img=1064282302"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Evgeny Biyatov /</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">1941-1945 年伟大卫国战争胜利 73 周年阅兵式上搭载高超音速 Kinzhal 火箭的多用途 MiG-31 战斗机</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="A multi-purpose MiG-31 fighter with the hypersonic Kinzhal rocket on the military parade devoted to the 73rd anniversary of the victory in the Great Patriotic War of 1941-1945  - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="在纪念 1941-1945 年伟大卫国战争胜利 73 周年的阅兵式上，搭载高超音速 Kinzhal 火箭的多用途 MiG-31 战斗机" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/106428/23/1064282303_0:158:3236:1978_1920x0_80_0_0_c4f03f23381435fcf1a7d1e675850ab6.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/106428/23/1064282303_0:158:3236:1978_640x0_80_0_0_6581ea187fae8ea27a851dfd58185959.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/106428/23/1064282303_0:158:3236:1978_1280x0_80_0_0_9352d2c60673574c1433c9b16c12b409.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/106428/23/1064282303_0:158:3236:1978_1920x0_80_0_0_c4f03f23381435fcf1a7d1e675850ab6.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Evgeny Biyatov /</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="s150x150" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="Oleg Burunov - Sputnik International" title="奥列格布鲁诺夫" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/09/0b/1080424846_0:0:2048:2048_100x100_80_0_0_3d7b461f8a98586fa3fe739930816aea.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">奥列格布鲁诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_burunov_oleg/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:o.burunov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">总统弗拉基米尔普京早些时候警告说，如果西方向乌克兰提供爱国者系统，这些防空系统将被摧毁。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯国防部 (MoD) 发言人 Igor Konashenkov 周二在一份声明中宣布，驻扎在基辅的美制<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230511/us-patriot-system-not-capable-of-intercepting-russian-kinzhal-missile---source-1110264588.html" target="_blank">MIM-104 爱国者</a>地对空导弹 (SAM) 系统被 Kinzhal（“匕首”）高超音速导弹击中弹道式导弹。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>根据声明，Kinzhal 是在俄罗斯武装部队“使用远程精确制导空基和海基武器对 AFU [乌克兰武装部队] 部队以及弹药库进行联合攻击时发射的、西方国家提供的武器和军事装备。”</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">那么，作为俄罗斯在乌克兰正在进行的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230516/russias-special-military-operation-in-ukraine-and-how-it-is-progressing-1105665248.html" target="_blank">特别军事行动的</a>一部分，对爱国者的 Kinzhal 罢工有什么了解呢？<em><strong>人造卫星</strong>探索</em>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2"> “被空中伏击击中”</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">消息灵通人士在接受俄罗斯卫星通讯社采访时表示，俄罗斯配备“猛击”导弹的超音速拦截机MiG-31K像晴天霹雳一样击中了驻扎在基辅的美国地对空导弹。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “由于 Kinzhal 的速度，爱国者系统突然遭到空中伏击。敌人的战斗人员无力保护他们的防空系统，”消息人士说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110418058" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/nutcracker-what-we-know-about-russias-kinzhal-hitting-us-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110418058.html?share-block=1110418350" data-title="&amp;quot;Due to the Kinzhal&amp;#x27;s speed, the Patriot system was suddenly hit from an air ambush. The enemy’s combat crew were powerless to protect their anti-aircraft system,&amp;quot; the source said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social" data-social="telegram"><div class="article__tg"></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据内部人士称，Kinzhal 能够在几分钟内到达目标，这就是爱国者机组人员根本没有时间改变位置或重新装载 SAM 发射器的原因。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2"> &#39;绝望的姿态&#39;</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯媒体援引莫斯科军事专家<em>阿列克谢·列昂科夫</em>的话说，MIM-104用尽了所有弹药，试图击落“猎豹”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他挑出了总共 32 枚爱国者导弹拦截器，这些拦截器是从 SAM 的八个发射器发射的，目的是击落 Kinzhal，但无济于事。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “结果，俄罗斯的高超音速导弹摧毁了爱国者的心脏——一个雷达和一个控制中心，这使得 SAM 变成了无用的军事硬件。[…] 32 枚导弹是一个非常大的弹药。事实爱国者向 Kinzhal 发射了所有这些拦截器，表明该系统相对于俄罗斯高超音速复合体的效率完全低下，”列昂科夫说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110418058" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/nutcracker-what-we-know-about-russias-kinzhal-hitting-us-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110418058.html?share-block=1110418445" data-title="&amp;quot;As a result, the Russian hypersonic missile destroyed the heart of the Patriot – a radar and a control center, something that has turned the SAM into a useless piece of military hardware. […] 32 missiles are a very massive round. The fact that the Patriot fired all those interceptors at the Kinzhal indicates the system&amp;#x27;s complete inefficiency in relation to the Russian hypersonic complex,&amp;quot; Leonkov said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他补充说，爱国者号机组人员发射的 32 枚拦截器是“一种绝望的表现，而不是专业人士的行为。”顺便说一句，发射一枚爱国者拦截器价值高达<strong>三百万美元</strong>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">与此同时，基辅否认<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230309/russian-military-conducts-massive-retaliatory-strike-in-ukraine-in-response-to-bryansk-terror-1108210949.html" target="_blank">俄罗斯高超音速导弹</a>击中了 MIM-104，乌克兰空军发言人 Yury Ignat 声称，“不要担心爱国者的命运。用某种‘Kinzhal’摧毁该系统是不可能的。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">俄罗斯国防部长嘲笑基辅的荒诞故事</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯国防部长谢尔盖·绍伊古周二独家告诉卫星通讯社，基辅有关据称<strong>击落六枚俄罗斯“金扎尔”高超音速导弹的</strong>说法是不真实的。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “我之前已经说过，我会再重复一遍：我们每次发射的 Kinzhal 导弹都没有他们在声明中声称的那样多。而且，这些‘乌克兰拦截’的数量是我们发射的三倍。他们总是弄错导弹的类型。这就是他们没有击中导弹的原因，”绍伊古指出，并补充说，“谁真正控制”了乌克兰的爱国者系统，这是一个很大的问号。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110418058" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/nutcracker-what-we-know-about-russias-kinzhal-hitting-us-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110418058.html?share-block=1110418634" data-title="&amp;quot;I have already said it before and I will repeat it again: we have not launched as many Kinzhal missiles as they allegedly shoot down in their statements every time. Moreover, the number of these &amp;#x27;Ukrainian interceptions&amp;#x27; exceeds our launches by three times. And they mistake the type of missiles all the time. That&amp;#x27;s why they don&amp;#x27;t hit them,” Shoigu pointed out, adding that there’s a big question mark over &amp;quot;who really controls&amp;quot; the Patriot systems in Ukraine."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">评估对爱国者 SAM 的 Kinzhal 攻击</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯国防部长发表讲话时，一家美国广播公司援引一位不愿透露姓名的白宫消息人士的话称，华盛顿仍在评估<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20220219/russian-aerospace-force-successfully-launches-kinzhal-hypersonic-missiles-during-drills-1093174539.html" target="_blank">Kinzhal 袭击对基辅 MIM-104 的影响</a>。消息人士称，导弹袭击的结果是，SAM 被认为已被损坏，但并未被摧毁。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">乌克兰军队目前拥有两枚爱国者地对空导弹，一枚由美国交付，另一枚由德国和荷兰联合交付。这些交付是<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230516/us-military-aid-to-ukraine-may-dry-up-by-july--1110394267.html" target="_blank">西方国家对基辅军事援助</a>的一部分，在俄罗斯开始对乌克兰的特别军事行动后不久，援助力度进一步加大. </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>这家美国广播公司在这方面报道称，“目前尚不清楚这些系统中的哪些系统可能遭到破坏 [在基辅]，但在俄罗斯的紧张局势加剧的情况下，让其中一个系统失效 - 即使是短期的 - 可能会影响乌克兰保卫乌克兰首都的能力导弹袭击。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110418058" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/nutcracker-what-we-know-about-russias-kinzhal-hitting-us-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110418058.html?share-block=1110418635" data-title="The US broadcaster reported in this context that, &amp;quot;It is unclear which of those systems was potentially damaged [in Kiev], but taking one out of commission – even for a short period – could affect Ukraine’s ability to defend the Ukrainian capital amid intensifying Russian missile attacks.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">另一家美国新闻媒体援引一位不愿透露姓名的白宫官员的话说，华盛顿和基辅“已经在讨论修复[爱国者]系统的最佳方法，目前看来该系统似乎不必从乌克兰移除。 “这位官员补充说，美国“将在未来几天有更好的了解”，并且“信息可能会随着时间的推移而改变”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">碰撞，繁荣，爆炸</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">就俄罗斯高超音速导弹袭击的后果而言，驻莫斯科的国际关系和安全分析师<em>马克·斯莱博达</em>告诉卫星通讯社，“爱国者号可能受到不止一次 [Kinzhal] 影响”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “你看到爱国者炸毁了它的负载。然后几秒钟后，就在那些导弹来自的地方，你看到了轰隆声，基辅夜空中的大闪光。看起来它是[的一部分] MIM-104] 电池被损坏或毁坏。我们不确切知道，但很明显这是一次打击，”Sleboda 指出，指的是 Kinzhal 罢工的视频。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110418058" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/nutcracker-what-we-know-about-russias-kinzhal-hitting-us-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110418058.html?share-block=1110418636" data-title="&amp;quot;Your saw the Patriot blow its load. And then a few seconds later, right where those missiles were coming from, you see the boom, the big flash of light filling the Kiev night sky. And it appears that it were parts of the [MIM-104] battery that were damaged or destroyed. We don&amp;#x27;t know exactly, but it seems pretty clear that it was a hit,&amp;quot; Sleboda pointed out, referring to the video of the Kinzhal strike."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">不难破解</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">2022 年 12 月， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20220901/russias-special-operation-isnt-aggression-merely-putting-end-to-kievs-war-on-own-people-putin-1100274278.html" target="_blank">俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京</a>评论了五角大楼向乌克兰交付爱国者系统的计划，基辅于今年春天收到了该系统。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>美国“现在说他们可以把爱国者 [in Ukraine]。好吧，让他们去做吧。我们也会破解爱国者 [like a nut]，并且需要在其位置安装一些东西，需要新系统有待开发 - 这是一个复杂而漫长的过程，”普京当时在俄罗斯国务院会议后告诉记者。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110418058" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/nutcracker-what-we-know-about-russias-kinzhal-hitting-us-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110418058.html?share-block=1110418637" data-title="The US is &amp;quot;now saying that they can put a Patriot [in Ukraine]. Okay, let them do it. We will crack the Patriot [like a nut] too, and something will need to be installed in its place, new systems need to be developed - this is a complex and lengthy process,&amp;quot; Putin told reporters after a meeting of the Russian State Council at the time."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “我们的对手认为这应该是一种防御性武器。好吧，我们会牢记这一点。而且总能找到解毒剂，”俄罗斯总统强调，并保证爱国者的交付将“徒劳无功” ”，并且会“只会延长冲突，仅此而已。”</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 14:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/nutcracker-what-we-know-about-russias-kinzhal-hitting-us-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110418058.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/nutcracker-what-we-know-about-russias-kinzhal-hitting-us-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110418058.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>我们</category><category>特别行动</category><category>Kinzhal 导弹系统</category><category>米格-31</category><category>攻击</category><category>罢工</category><category>爱国者导弹系统</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Leave 'La-la-land': Musk Slams Big Tech's 'Laptop Class' Over Remote Work]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110416206" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/0c/1109375196_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_902954f1f0ad09ad1c87beddc311c578.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1109375178" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/leave-la-la-land-musk-slams-big-techs-laptop-class-over-remote-work-1110416206.html?share-img=1109375178"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Susan Walsh</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">特斯拉、SpaceX 和 Twitter 首席执行官埃隆·马斯克。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Tesla, SpaceX, and Twitter CEO Elon Musk. - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="特斯拉、SpaceX 和 Twitter 首席执行官埃隆·马斯克。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/0c/1109375196_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_af8506b3c7e71e815539013eaf0e9619.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/0c/1109375196_0:160:3072:1888_640x0_80_0_0_a08335f382c9b0b4453cf780943045a7.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/0c/1109375196_0:160:3072:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_9b9c80b4dae6175f8ae500ed61c5c38a.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/0c/1109375196_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_af8506b3c7e71e815539013eaf0e9619.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / 苏珊·沃尔什</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">谢尔盖·列别杰夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_lebedev_sergey/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:s.lebedev@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">在接受一家美国媒体采访时，埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 加入了持续不断的远程工作趋势，在 COVID 封锁时代，他称之为大型科技公司和跨国公司的“笔记本电脑阶层”引领了这一趋势，他抨击了他们的虚伪，让这种趋势一直持续到现在服务人员必须现身做实际工作。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">亿万富翁企业家埃隆·马斯克猛烈抨击科技专业人士坚持在家工作的习惯，并加倍严厉批评，称他们为“生活在洛杉矶的笔记本电脑阶层”，被媒体引用。除了明显的生产力问题外，他还列举了道德原因。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">马斯克认为，软件工程师很虚伪，希望在家工作，同时期望服务人员继续亲自出现。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">他甚至提到了假的玛丽·安托瓦内特 (Marie Antoinette) 名言，“让他们吃蛋糕吧。” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>这位科技大亨提到了法国最后一位女王玛丽·安托瓦内特 (Marie Antoinette)，她建议农民在得知自己快要饿死且没有面包时“吃蛋糕”。这句话虽然被认为是骗局，但却成为虚伪的象征。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">马斯克以建议程序员结束他的咆哮结束了“他们在家工作的胡说八道**”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在 COVID 锁定期间，远程工作趋势成为强制性趋势，许多人已经习惯了。然而，随着生产力下降和投资者兴趣增加，许多科技公司开始积极敦促员工返回办公室。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">当马斯克在 2022 年秋天收购 Twitter 时，他立即禁止远程工作，并表示员工每周必须在办公室工作 40 小时。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在马斯克的领导下，Twitter 经历了许多变化，从付费验证复选标记开始，到新闻源中推出“为你”部分，到现在著名的 Twitter 文件的披露结束。后者是一大堆文件，揭示了该平台与美国政府合作并粉饰“深层政府”审查制度的令人不快的真相。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 14:17:15 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/leave-la-la-land-musk-slams-big-techs-laptop-class-over-remote-work-1110416206.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/leave-la-la-land-musk-slams-big-techs-laptop-class-over-remote-work-1110416206.html<category>超越政治</category><category>埃隆·马斯克</category><category>美国经济</category><category>推特</category><category>特斯拉</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Lavrov Slams West's Regrets Over Peace Talks as Ukraine Refuses to Negotiate]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110417364" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/1d/1109945843_0:0:3007:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_2e50c5204f245a9ace9bbb80d5325947.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1109945825" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/zelensky-is-who-refuses-to-do-diplomacy-not-russia--lavrov-1110417364.html?share-img=1109945825"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Aleksey Nikolskyi</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖拉夫罗夫</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Russian Foreign Minister Sergey Lavrov - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="俄罗斯外长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/1d/1109945843_0:0:3008:1691_1920x0_80_0_0_a338ecb2911dde916b1a001b79ef1e24.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/1d/1109945843_0:0:3008:1691_640x0_80_0_0_7de8396af0121cc1ff141e887e7c980a.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/1d/1109945843_0:0:3008:1691_1280x0_80_0_0_8855311576ec3b6387779562c57555d4.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/04/1d/1109945843_0:0:3008:1691_1920x0_80_0_0_a338ecb2911dde916b1a001b79ef1e24.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Aleksey Nikolskyi</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">基辅通过了一项特别法律，阻止与克里姆林宫进行任何和平谈判，同时对俄罗斯领土进行恐怖袭击并牺牲无数乌克兰人的生命。然而，西方的政治言论声称，正是莫斯科在回避外交。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖拉夫罗夫表示，他厌倦了回应华盛顿关于莫斯科不想与基辅进行对话的言论。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">拉夫罗夫在评论最近有关拉丁美洲和非洲国家为乌克兰制定和平计划的报道时强调，在与白俄罗斯外长谢尔盖·阿列尼克的联合记者会上，俄罗斯尚未收到任何倡议。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “我们回应了拉丁美洲和非洲朋友向我们发出的呼吁，我们准备考虑他们的任何提议（关于乌克兰危机），这些提议是出于帮助稳定世界秩序的真诚愿望，但到目前为止，与我们的中国邻国不同，我们没有从巴西人或非洲人的纸面上看到任何东西，”俄罗斯高级外交官说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110417364" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/zelensky-is-who-refuses-to-do-diplomacy-not-russia--lavrov-1110417364.html?share-block=1110417366" data-title="&amp;quot;We responded to an appeal to us from Latin American and African friends that we are ready to consider any of their proposals [on the crisis in Ukraine], which are dictated by a sincere desire to help stabilize the world order, but so far, we have not seen anything on paper either from the Brazilians or from the Africans, unlike from our Chinese neighbors,&amp;quot; Russian top diplomat stated."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位部长还谴责了法国总统埃马纽埃尔马克龙最近关于俄罗斯对中国“依赖”的声明。在接受采访时，这位法国总统声称俄罗斯遭受了“地缘政治失败”并变得依赖北京，从而在其历史盟友中“引起怀疑”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>拉夫罗夫声称：“至于马克龙关于附庸主宰的言论，你知道这是弗洛伊德式的：‘什么伤人，这就是他所说的’。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110417364" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/zelensky-is-who-refuses-to-do-diplomacy-not-russia--lavrov-1110417364.html?share-block=1110417369" data-title="&amp;quot;As for Macron&amp;#x27;s statements about the vassal-master, you know it is Freudian: &amp;#x27;What hurts, that is what he talks about&amp;#x27;,&amp;quot; Lavrov alleged."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位法国领导人多年来一直以宣布欧盟的战略自主权而闻名，但众所周知，美国不会允许欧盟拥有任何战略或任何类型的自主权，部长添加。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">拉夫罗夫还强调，北约的扩大破坏了欧洲安全对话的前景。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>拉夫罗夫总结说：“北约不计后果地向东扩张，而且向北和其他地理方向扩张，破坏了就欧洲安全进行任何进一步正常对话的前景。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110417364" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/zelensky-is-who-refuses-to-do-diplomacy-not-russia--lavrov-1110417364.html?share-block=1110417372" data-title="&amp;quot;The reckless expansion of NATO not only eastward, but also northward and in other geographic directions undermines the very prospect of any further normal conversation about European security,&amp;quot; Lavrov concluded."></div></div></div></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 13:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/zelensky-is-who-refuses-to-do-diplomacy-not-russia--lavrov-1110417364.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/zelensky-is-who-refuses-to-do-diplomacy-not-russia--lavrov-1110417364.html<category>俄罗斯</category><category>谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫</category><category>北约扩张</category><category>马克龙</category><category>俄罗斯-北约摊牌</category><category>乌克兰危机</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[US Senator Fears Artificial Intelligence Could Make Him 'Endorse Putin']]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110414889" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/08/1110205255_0:0:1456:816_1440x900_80_0_1_e4d0110282ed36e057df46f1ac355711.png?source-sid=cc_0" data-photoview-image-id="1110205237" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/us-senator-fears-artificial-intelligence-could-make-him-endorse-putin-1110414889.html?share-img=1110205237"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright"><a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> //</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">AI接管世界</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="cc_0" alt="AI Taking over the world - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="人工智能接管世界" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/08/1110205255_3:0:1454:816_1920x0_80_0_0_1fcf5a9f4972c2af13ac1979e47fbfd9.png" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/08/1110205255_3:0:1454:816_640x0_80_0_0_c25696b1c12775db1fcbe9967aa63102.png 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/08/1110205255_3:0:1454:816_1280x0_80_0_0_b70cb15675765f1c322b1d1a8dcb5146.png 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/08/1110205255_3:0:1454:816_1920x0_80_0_0_1fcf5a9f4972c2af13ac1979e47fbfd9.png 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> <a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> / / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="s150x150" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="James Tweedie - Sputnik International" title="詹姆斯·特威迪" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e4/08/1c/1080307270_0:3:397:400_100x100_80_0_0_7777393b9b18802f2e3c5eaa9cbcc612.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">詹姆斯·特威迪</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tweedie_james/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:j.tweedie@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">先进人工智能的问题似乎将取代“俄罗斯干涉”成为华盛顿政治精英的妖怪，但其他人提出的担忧与科幻小说中的概念相呼应，例如终结者的天网防御计算机。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国参议院委员会获悉，人工智能 (AI) 软件可用于将话语送入政客之口。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">周二，康涅狄格州民主党参议员理查德·布卢门撒尔 (Richard Blumenthal) 在参议院司法委员会的小组委员会听证会上就这一新兴科技现象展开了听证会，他询问在线人工智能“聊天机器人” <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230411/us-mulls-mandatory-monitoring-of-ai-programs-like-chatgpt-reports-say-1109351272.html" target="_blank">ChatGPT</a>认为他应该如何在房间里发言。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该软件开始发表自己编写的演讲，模仿他的声音。这位参议员承认他印象深刻——但也担心它会被用来冒充和错误引用他的话。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “如果我问过它，如果它提供了对乌克兰投降或<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230509/putin-a-war-has-been-unleashed-against-russia-but-moscow-will-tackle-it--1110212663.html" target="_blank">弗拉基米尔普京领导的</a>认可怎么办？”布卢门撒尔问道。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110414889" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/us-senator-fears-artificial-intelligence-could-make-him-endorse-putin-1110414889.html?share-block=1110416469" data-title="&amp;quot;What if I had asked it, and what if it had provided, an endorsement of Ukraine surrendering or Vladimir Putin&amp;#x27;s leadership?&amp;quot; Blumenthal asked."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> ChatGPT 的开发商 OpenAI 的首席执行官 Sam Altman 在听证会上作证。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “随着这项技术的进步，我们了解到人们对它如何改变我们的生活方式感到焦虑。我们也是，”奥特曼说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">委员会主席、伊利诺伊州资深民主党参议员迪克·德宾 (Dick Durbin) 表示，政府应该成立一个新机构来<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230411/us-mulls-mandatory-monitoring-of-ai-programs-like-chatgpt-reports-say-1109351272.html" target="_blank">监管 AI 技术。</a> </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “我们正在处理不一定有边界的创新。我们可能会创建一个伟大的美国机构 - 我希望我们这样做 - 可能对美国公司和美国活动没有管辖权有什么东西会从外面轰炸我们，”德宾说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110414889" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/us-senator-fears-artificial-intelligence-could-make-him-endorse-putin-1110414889.html?share-block=1110417320" data-title="&amp;quot;We&amp;#x27;re dealing with innovation that doesn’t necessarily have a boundary. We may create a great US agency — and I hope that we do — that may have jurisdiction over US corporations and US activity that doesn’t have a thing to do with what’s gonna bombard us from outside,&amp;quot; Durbin said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">南卡罗来纳州共和党参议员 Lindsey Graham 是该委员会的高级成员，他支持监管机构为 AI 系统颁发许可证的想法。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">奥尔特曼后来告诉记者，他支持这两项提议——将它们与国际原子能机构 (IAEA) 进行了不祥的比较，国际原子能机构是负责执行《不扩散核武器条约》(NPT) 的联合国机构。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “这很难。这听起来有点天真，”这位 OpenAI 老板说。 “但我们已经为其他行业做到了。国际原子能机构做到了。我认为这是一项我们应该认真对待的技术。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110414889" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/us-senator-fears-artificial-intelligence-could-make-him-endorse-putin-1110414889.html?share-block=1110416539" data-title="&amp;quot;It&amp;#x27;s difficult. It sounds sort of like a naïve thing,&amp;quot; the OpenAI boss said. &amp;quot;But we’ve done it for other industries. IAEA did it. And I think this is a technology we should treat with that level of seriousness.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">密苏里州共和党参议员乔什·霍利此前曾主张对社交媒体科技公司进行更严格的监管，而 2020 年民主党总统初选候选人艾米·克洛布查尔也曾表示担心人工智能可能被用来<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230419/elon-musk-ais-could-undermine-democracy-if-used-in-elections-1109643011.html" target="_blank">影响选民</a>并在竞选期间传播错误信息。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “这是我最关心的领域之一——这些模型更普遍的操纵、说服、提供某种一对一虚假信息的能力，”奥特曼回应道。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110414889" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/us-senator-fears-artificial-intelligence-could-make-him-endorse-putin-1110414889.html?share-block=1110417321" data-title="&quot;It's one of my areas of greatest concerns — the more general capability of these models to manipulate, to persuade, to provide sort of one-on-one disinformation,&quot; Altman responded."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">纽约大学教授加里马库斯是一位心理学家和认知科学家，他呼吁<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230404/just-identify-tricky-areas-bill-gates-opposes-pausing-ai-beyond-gpt-4-hypes-huge-benefits-1109119337.html" target="_blank">暂停</a>AI 开发六个月以评估可能的风险，他也将在委员会作证。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 12:38:58 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/us-senator-fears-artificial-intelligence-could-make-him-endorse-putin-1110414889.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/us-senator-fears-artificial-intelligence-could-make-him-endorse-putin-1110414889.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>科学与技术</category><category>大科技</category><category>人工智能</category><category>人工智能 (AI)</category><category>理查德·布卢门撒尔</category><category>弗拉基米尔普京</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>参议院</category><category>病毒性的</category><category>聊天GPT</category><category>迪克德宾</category><category>开放人工智能</category><category>国际原子能机构 (IAEA)</category><category>不扩散核武器条约 (NPT)</category><category>核不扩散条约 (NPT)</category><category>华盛顿</category><category>美国参议院司法委员会</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Erdogan to Prioritize TV Appearances in Preparation for Presidential Runoff - Reports]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110416330" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0e/1110352968_0:0:3033:1969_1440x900_80_0_1_363b58889c4dfb8c0dd99b5dc2b47198.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110352950" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/erdogan-to-prioritize-tv-appearances-in-preparation-for-presidential-runoff---reports-1110416330.html?share-img=1110352950"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Pavel Bednyakov</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">土耳其总统塔伊普埃尔多安在总统和议会选举期间走在投票站投票</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Turkish President Tayyip Erdogan walks at a polling station to vote during the presidential and parliamentary elections - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="土耳其总统塔伊普埃尔多安在总统和议会选举期间走在投票站投票" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0e/1110352968_0:0:3033:1706_1920x0_80_0_0_935b5f22695213b10f469fc67eb82cf1.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0e/1110352968_0:0:3033:1706_640x0_80_0_0_d7a745df1edd30ac1d88235804f14a4d.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0e/1110352968_0:0:3033:1706_1280x0_80_0_0_6b27ba8b36e938c5f162f69ca4e48040.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0e/1110352968_0:0:3033:1706_1920x0_80_0_0_935b5f22695213b10f469fc67eb82cf1.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / 帕维尔贝德尼亚科夫</div>/ </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据安卡拉（人造卫星）网报道：土耳其媒体周三报道，现任土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安将专注于出现在电视节目中并访问受 2 月地震影响最严重的地区，为总统决选做准备。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据土耳其报纸报道，这位土耳其领导人已经指示执政的正义与发展党（也称为 AK 党）的所有机构在此过程中都在实地，并且“不要放松”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">埃尔多安的主要竞争对手 Kemal Kilicdaroglu 也计划在第二轮选举前访问地震灾区并参加各种电视节目，但这一次，他的演讲将主要集中在更强大的社会计划和反恐斗争上，报道称。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Turkiye 的反对派认为，它未能充分反击描绘它与库尔德工人党（PKK）“并肩作战”的“政府宣传”，库尔德工人党寻求在 Turkiye 建立库尔德自治，并被安卡拉列为恐怖分子，该报报道。反对派计划特别注意转移此类指控，为决选做准备。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “我们的主席 [Kilicdaroglu] 和我们都将发出强烈信号，表明我们反对一切形式的恐怖主义，”新闻媒体援引土耳其主要反对党共和人民党的消息人士的话说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在清点完 100% 的选票后，土耳其最高选举委员会周一宣布，由于没有候选人达到 50% 的门槛，第二轮总统选举将于 5 月 28 日举行。第一轮，埃尔多安获得 49.51% 的选票，基利达罗格鲁获得 44.88% 的选票。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 11:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/erdogan-to-prioritize-tv-appearances-in-preparation-for-presidential-runoff---reports-1110416330.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/erdogan-to-prioritize-tv-appearances-in-preparation-for-presidential-runoff---reports-1110416330.html<category>世界</category><category>突厥耶</category><category>雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安</category><category>2023 年土耳其总统选举</category></item></channel></rss>